data.description: Discover this fantastic gem on a spacious lot, perfect for outdoor fun and poolside hangouts. With a two-car garage and a front driveway, parking is a breeze for your crew.Step inside and soak in the open vibe, complete with "trey" ceilings and elegant crown molding. The kitchen's stainless steel appliances and sleek granite countertops are as stylish as your dance moves. A 2015 update adds modern flair.But wait, there's more! This home boasts newly refinished hardwood floors that gleam with sophistication. The interior and exterior have received fresh coats of paint, giving the whole place a brand-new, inviting look.Get ready to host epic gatherings. The gated pool is your new party HQ, where you can chill, splash, and make memories.No worries about flooding here. This property's got you covered. Your Houston dream home is waiting to make homeownership seriously rad.
